data.description: Lovely, Spacious One Bedroom with One Bath Condo. Clean, move-in ready! Open floor plan. This ACTIVE 55+ Five Towns community offers numerous activities, including six pools (two are heated), tennis courts, shuffle board courts, billiard's club and more. Close to shopping, Gulf Beaches, and all that Downtown St. Petersburg has to offer! Unit has updated electrical panel and outlets. Gas, Water, Garbage, Sewer, WiFi/Cable, use of Pools, Clubhouse and Recreation Facilities all included in association fees. Must see!
